channel.title: Add custom models to your server
channel.description:
[b]Ever wanted custom items on your server?[/b] [b]Ever wanted The new hp bar? or a custom login sprite?[/b] [b]Than this tutorial is something for you![/b]
[b]Hello, my name is Alex. Today i'm gonna show you how to download and put models on your client. Pictures included. We will do the following things:[/b]
[b]Models[/b]
[ul][li]Download a model from the model section.[/li] [li]Put them in your model folder.[/li] [li]Add the ints.[/li][/ul]
Ok lets start. First download a model from the model section. [IMG]http://i45.tinypic.com/2edrt4y.jpg[/img]
Pick 1 up and download it. [IMG]http://i46.tinypic.com/2i7bs5h.jpg[/img]
Save them in a folder. [IMG]http://i47.tinypic.com/vs2lag.jpg[/img]
Put them in the right place. [IMG]http://i45.tinypic.com/r7knwj.jpg[/img]
Credits: Me for writing this tutorial You guys for having time to watch this
Please do not flame it was my first tutorial.
